race.comment: ROJO MOLLY (1) broke a string of placings finishing in the money two on end before a last start fifth (25.99) at this track. Solid record at this trip including two wins. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings two times from three starts. Looks the one to beat on her best form. JUNGLE BOOGIE (5) is progressing well and looks close to another win after hitting the frame last run (35.09) at Launceston. Has a strong record out of this box with three wins and two minor placings from seven starts. Will give a great sight again. SYDNEY DANGER (8) was safely held last time out, finishing fifth at this track over 340m behind Rojo Jojo (26.08) in a Grade 5. Was in the money the start prior. The form out of the last run is proven to be strong. Key runner who gets his chance to atone. BILLIE BENSON (3) was in the money last start from this box and should feature again.
